function distribute(numeroCartas)
    deck = getDeck("344f75")
    if pcall(checkDeckQuantity,deck,numeroCartas[1]) then

    else
        recoverDiscards(deck,numeroCartas[1])
    end

function getDeck(ID)
    deckArea = getObjectFromGUID(ID)
    deck = deckArea.getObjects()
    return deck[1]
end


function checkDeckQuantity(deck,numeroCartas)

    if unexpected_condition then error() end
    count = 0

    for k,card in ipairs(deck.getObjects()) do
        count = count+1
    end

    if numeroCartas > count then
        recoverDiscards(deck,numeroCartas)
    else
        dealHand(deck,numeroCartas)
    end



end

function recoverDiscards(deck,numeroCartas)
    deckPosition = deck.getPosition()
    discards = getDeck("73430b")
    discards.flip()
    discards.randomize()
    discards.setPosition(deckPosition)
    deckPosition.y = 10
    deck.setPosition(deckPosition)
    --newDeck = getDeck("110203")
    --dealHand(newDeck,numeroCartas)

end


function dealHand(deck,numeroCartas)
    if unexpected_condition then error() end
    targetPos, targetRot = deck.getPosition(), deck.getRotation()
    targetPos.y = 3
    targetPos.x = targetPos.x + 8
    for i=1, numeroCartas do
        deck.takeObject({index = 0, position = targetPos, rotation = targetRot, flip=true})
        targetPos.x = targetPos.x + 6
    end

end

    self.createButton({
      label="", click_function="repairMarket", function_owner=self,
      position={0,0,0}, height=325, width=325, font_size=0, rotation={0,0,0}
    })

function repairMarket()
    marketDeck = getDeck("964ce4")
    marketDeckPosition = marketDeck.getPosition()
    card1 = getDeck("1fa492")
    card2 = getDeck("7b55e1")
    card3 = getDeck("57473f")
    card4 = getDeck("f74dfe")
    card5 = getDeck("a61b5b")

    if card1 == nil then
        marketDeckPosition.x = -14
        marketDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = marketDeckPosition, flip=true})
    end

    if card2 == nil then
        marketDeckPosition.x = -8
        marketDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = marketDeckPosition, flip=true})
    end

    if card3 == nil then
        marketDeckPosition.x = -2
        marketDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = marketDeckPosition, flip=true})
    end

    if card4 == nil then
        marketDeckPosition.x = 4
        marketDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = marketDeckPosition, flip=true})
    end

    if card5 == nil then
        marketDeckPosition.x = 10
        marketDeck.takeObject({index = 0, position = marketDeckPosition, flip=true})
    end

end

function getDeck(ID)
    deckArea = getObjectFromGUID(ID)
    deck = deckArea.getObjects()
    return deck[1]
end

function onLoad()
    self.interactable = false;
    self.createButton({
    label = "CUSTOMIZE BOARD",
    click_function = "onButtonClick",
    function_owner = self,
    width = 750,
    height = 75,
    color = {1, 1, 1, 1.0},
    position = {-15.5, 10, -5},
    rotation = {180, 270, 80},
    font_size = 75
})
end

function onButtonClick()
    if self.interactable == false then
        self.interactable = true;
        self.setColorTint({1, 1, 1})
        self.editButton({ label = "LOCK BOARD" })

    else
        self.interactable = false;
        self.editButton({ label = "CUSTOMIZE BOARD"})

    end
end

2.Name: Custom_Assetbundle
2.Description: Click on the handle to close.
2.LuaScript:
local ConcealedStorageHeight = 3.0
local ConceiledStorageOffset = 10000.0
local StorageState = 1

local BB = {
	Min = {
		x = -16.0,
		y = 41.99,
		z = -50.0
	},
	Max = {
		x = 16.0,
		y = 41.99,
		z = -32.0
	}
}

function onLoad()
    self.interactable = false;
	
    self.createButton({
		label = "",
		click_function = "onButtonClick",
		function_owner = self,
		width = 1000,
		height = 750,
		color = {1, 0, 0, 0.0},
		position = {0, 40.7, 50.5},
		rotation = {-90, 0, 0},
		font_size = 200
    })
	
	if self.getStateId() ~= StorageState then
    Timer.create({
        identifier = ("onAfterLoad" .. self.guid),
        function_name = "onAfterLoad",
        delay = 0.2
    })
	end
end

function onAfterLoad()
	local pos = self.getPosition()
	local bounds = self.getBoundsNormalized()
	local rot = self.getRotation()
	local direction = 1.0
	
	if rot.y == 0 then
		direction = -1.0
	end
	
	BB.Min.x = BB.Min.x + pos.x
	BB.Min.y = BB.Min.y + pos.y - 1.5
	BB.Min.z = (BB.Min.z * direction) + pos.z
	
	BB.Max.x = 	BB.Max.x + pos.x
	BB.Max.y = 	BB.Max.y + pos.y + ConcealedStorageHeight + 0.5
	BB.Max.z = (BB.Max.z * direction) + pos.z
	
	HideObjectsAbove( false )
end

function onButtonClick()
	local currentState = self.getStateId()
	local nextState = 1 + (currentState % 2)
	
	if currentState ~= StorageState then
		HideObjectsAbove( true )
	end
	
	self.setState( nextState )
end

function HideObjectsAbove( toggle )
    local objectsAbove = {}
	local BBMin = { x = BB.Min.x, y = BB.Min.y, z = BB.Min.z }
	local BBMax = { x = BB.Max.x, y = BB.Max.y, z = BB.Max.z }
	
	if not toggle then
		BBMin.y = BBMin.y - ConceiledStorageOffset
		BBMax.y = BBMax.y - ConceiledStorageOffset
	end
    
    for k,v in pairs( getAllObjects() ) do
        if v != self then
            if PointToAABBIntersect( BBMin, BBMax, v.getPosition() ) then
                if toggle then
                    Store( v )
                else
                    Dispense( v )
                end
            end
        end
    end
end

-- Assumes ||min|| < ||max||
function PointToAABBIntersect( min, max, point )
    if IsInRange( point.x, min.x, max.x ) and
       IsInRange( point.y, min.y, max.y ) and
       IsInRange( point.z, min.z, max.z ) then
	   return true
    end
    
    return false
end

function IsInRange( value, a, b )
	local min = 0
	local max = 0
	
	if a > b then
		max = a
		min = b
	else
		max = b
		min = a
	end
	
	if value > min and value < max then
		return true
	end
	
	return false
end

function Store( obj )
	local pos = obj.getPosition()
	local isLocked = obj.getLock()
	
	obj.setVar( "LockStatus", isLocked )
	
    obj.interactable = false
    obj.setLock( true )
    obj.setPosition({
        x = pos.x,
        y = pos.y - ConceiledStorageOffset,
        z = pos.z
    })
end

function Dispense( obj )
	local pos = obj.getPosition()
	local originalLockStatus = obj.getVar( "LockStatus" )
	
    obj.setPosition({
        x = pos.x,
        y = pos.y + ConceiledStorageOffset,
        z = pos.z
    })
	
    obj.interactable = true
	
	if originalLockStatus ~= nil and originalLockStatus == true then
		obj.setLock( true )
	else
		obj.setLock( false )
	end
end

       IsInRange( point.y, min.y, max.y ) and
       IsInRange( point.z, min.z, max.z ) then
	   return true
    end
    
    return false
end

function IsInRange( value, a, b )
	local min = 0
	local max = 0
	
	if a > b then
		max = a
		min = b
	else
		max = b
		min = a
	end
	
	if value > min and value < max then
		return true
	end
	
	return false
end

function Store( obj )
	local pos = obj.getPosition()
	local isLocked = obj.getLock()
	
	obj.setVar( "LockStatus", isLocked )
	
    obj.interactable = false
    obj.setLock( true )
    obj.setPosition({
        x = pos.x,
        y = pos.y - ConceiledStorageOffset,
        z = pos.z
    })
end

function Dispense( obj )
	local pos = obj.getPosition()
	local originalLockStatus = obj.getVar( "LockStatus" )
	
    obj.setPosition({
        x = pos.x,
        y = pos.y + ConceiledStorageOffset,
        z = pos.z
    })
	
    obj.interactable = true
	
	if originalLockStatus ~= nil and originalLockStatus == true then
		obj.setLock( true )
	else
		obj.setLock( false )
	end
end

local ConcealedStorageHeight = 3.0
local ConceiledStorageOffset = 10000.0
local StorageState = 1

local BB = {
	Min = {
		x = -16.0,
		y = 41.99,
		z = -50.0
	},
	Max = {
		x = 16.0,
		y = 41.99,
		z = -32.0
	}
}

function onLoad()
    self.interactable = false;
	
    self.createButton({
		label = "",
		click_function = "onButtonClick",
		function_owner = self,
		width = 1000,
		height = 750,
		color = {1, 0, 0, 0.0},
		position = {0, 40.7, 50.5},
		rotation = {-90, 0, 0},
		font_size = 200
    })
	
	if self.getStateId() ~= StorageState then
    Timer.create({
        identifier = ("onAfterLoad" .. self.guid),
        function_name = "onAfterLoad",
        delay = 0.2
    })
	end
end

function onAfterLoad()
	local pos = self.getPosition()
	local bounds = self.getBoundsNormalized()
	local rot = self.getRotation()
	local direction = 1.0
	
	if rot.y == 0 then
		direction = -1.0
	end
	
	BB.Min.x = BB.Min.x + pos.x
	BB.Min.y = BB.Min.y + pos.y - 1.5
	BB.Min.z = (BB.Min.z * direction) + pos.z
	
	BB.Max.x = 	BB.Max.x + pos.x
	BB.Max.y = 	BB.Max.y + pos.y + ConcealedStorageHeight + 0.5
	BB.Max.z = (BB.Max.z * direction) + pos.z
	
	HideObjectsAbove( false )
end

function onButtonClick()
	local currentState = self.getStateId()
	local nextState = 1 + (currentState % 2)
	
	if currentState ~= StorageState then
		HideObjectsAbove( true )
	end
	
	self.setState( nextState )
end

function HideObjectsAbove( toggle )
    local objectsAbove = {}
	local BBMin = { x = BB.Min.x, y = BB.Min.y, z = BB.Min.z }
	local BBMax = { x = BB.Max.x, y = BB.Max.y, z = BB.Max.z }
	
	if not toggle then
		BBMin.y = BBMin.y - ConceiledStorageOffset
		BBMax.y = BBMax.y - ConceiledStorageOffset
	end
    
    for k,v in pairs( getAllObjects() ) do
        if v != self then
            if PointToAABBIntersect( BBMin, BBMax, v.getPosition() ) then
                if toggle then
                    Store( v )
                else
                    Dispense( v )
                end
            end
        end
    end
end
